338
00:27:30,510 --> 00:27:32,470
since playing with you wasn't any fun.
♬  if you close your eyes ♬

339
00:27:32,510 --> 00:27:35,010
Come on, play with me.

340
00:27:35,050 --> 00:27:38,050
Forget it. ♬ And that would break my heart in two ♬

341
00:27:38,110 --> 00:27:41,550
The first person to fall asleep loses.

342
00:27:41,610 --> 00:27:44,730
When it come to fitness, it's Oh Ha Na.
♬ If I need you♬

